graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller]
        Operator[Operator Pod]
        Controller -->|manages| Operator
    end

    subgraph "DSP Stack Components"
        APIServer[DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>8887/TCP gRPC]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        WorkflowController[Argo Workflow Controller]

        MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP]
        MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP mTLS]

        APIServer -->|syncs status| PersistenceAgent
        APIServer -->|schedules| ScheduledWorkflow
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
    end

    subgraph "Storage Layer"
        MariaDB[(MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP)]
        Minio[(Minio<br/>9000/TCP S3 API)]
    end

    subgraph "Execution Layer"
        ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows<br/>v1alpha1]
        WorkflowPods[Workflow Pods]
        WorkflowController -->|creates| ArgoWorkflows
        ArgoWorkflows -->|executes| WorkflowPods
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPA[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPA -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|deploys| MLMDgRPC
    Controller -->|deploys| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|deploys| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|provisions| MariaDB
    Controller -->|provisions| Minio

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    APIServer -->|tracks ML metadata| MLMDgRPC

    PersistenceAgent -->|updates| MariaDB
    WorkflowPods -->|logs to| MLMDgRPC
    WorkflowPods -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    MLMDgRPC -->|persists| MariaDB

    APIServer -->|creates| ArgoWorkflows

    subgraph "CRDs Managed"
        DSPACrd[datasciencepipelinesapplications.opendatahub.io/v1]
        PipelineCrd[pipelines.kubeflow.org/v1]
        WorkflowCrd[argoproj.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/creates| DSPACrd
    Controller -->|watches/creates| PipelineCrd
    Controller -->|watches/creates| WorkflowCrd

    subgraph "External Services"
        ExternalDB[(External DB<br/>MySQL/MariaDB)]
        ExternalS3[(External S3<br/>ODF/AWS S3)]
    end

    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalDB
    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalS3

    subgraph "ODH Integrations"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI]
        KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]
        Ray[Ray<br/>RayCluster/RayJob]
        CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>AppWrapper]
    end

    Dashboard -->|manages pipelines| APIServer
    WorkflowPods -->|deploys models| KServe
    WorkflowPods -->|executes| Ray
    WorkflowPods -->|submits| CodeFlare

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2
    style PersistenceAgent fill:#4a90e2
    style ScheduledWorkflow fill:#4a90e2
    style WorkflowController fill:#4a90e2
    style MLMDgRPC fill:#4a90e2
    style MLMDEnvoy fill:#4a90e2
    style DSPA fill:#f5a623
    style DSPACrd fill:#f5a623
    style PipelineCrd fill:#f5a623
    style WorkflowCrd fill:#f5a623
    style MariaDB fill:#9b59b6
    style Minio fill:#9b59b6
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321
    style KServe fill:#7ed321
    style Ray fill:#7ed321
    style CodeFlare fill:#7ed321
